# Archive folders (keep directory structure, ignore generated HTML)
archive/news/*.html
archive/papers/*.html
archive/trending/*.html
archive/wechat_draft/*.html
archive/wechat_draft/*.md
archive/wechat_papers_weekly/*.html
archive/wechat_papers_weekly/*.md
